description:
Mike traveled through the Naruto world, became Jiraiya's apprentice, and activated the god-level comic system.

He knows that the water in the Naruto world is very deep, so he retreats to experience and strives to improve his strength.

After Konoha collapsed the plan, the three generations of Hokage were killed, and Jiraiya took Naruto to find Tsunade to succeed Hokage, so Mike replaced him as the acting Hokage temporarily.

More than a month later, when Jiraiya brought Tsunade back to Konoha, he was completely stunned!

Kakashi: Low Chakra doesn't matter, I use Zanpakutō anyway!

Might Guy: Can you add Super Saiyan mode after opening the eight gates?

Hyuga Hiashi: It turns out that the ultimate meaning of soft boxing is the extreme martial arts kick!

Sasuke: What kind of brother is Sharingan? Still easy to use!

...

Jiraiya: How long have I been away, you actually raised the strength of Ninja to be comparable to the Six Paths?!
